# Description of Drifter Design:

## Version 0:
- 12" length of 2.5" Schedule 40 (body),
- Schedule 80 slip x pipe-thread coupling
- Schedule 80 plug
- 12" length of 3/4" Schedule 80 (antennae)
- Ben to fill out remaining info...

## Version 1: Piston plug for sensor/antenae assembly (https://www.sealseastern.com/OringPistonSeal.asp)
- 2.5" ID:    2.455"--2.475"    ~ 2.465 +/- 0.011 
- Metric:     6.236cm--6.287cm	~ 6.262 +/- 0.026
- 3mm o-ring: 	     grove-depth ~ 2.25 mm 	    ID ~ 5.85cm
- 3.5mm o-ring:      grove-depth ~ 3.07 mm	    ID ~ 5.67cm
- 5mm o-ring: 	     grove-depth ~ 4.00 mm (80%)    ID ~ 5.33cm


Nominal ID:
- 2.47"--2.475" -> 62.75mm--62.87mm

Plug Diameter (smaller by 0.01" ~ 0.25 mm):
2.46" ~ 62.5mm

Oring Thickness: 0.138" -> 3.5mm
groove_depth = 2.45mm
grove_width  = 1.03*oring_thickness

First Print:
John's printer: plug diameter = 2.445" ~ 62.103 mm
CMS's printer: 	plug diameter = 2.454" ~ 62.332 mm

## Threaded insert for set-screw:

1) Heat-Set: https://www.mcmaster.com/products/threaded-inserts/for-use-in~plastic-1/heat-set-threaded-inserts-for-plastic~~/
2) Twist-Resistant Press-In: https://www.mcmaster.com/92398A125/



